metadata.name: Lucky Girl Syndrome
metadata.description:
Working hard to be "lucky" ...

This piece started off as an intuitive painting, then became a digital illustration, and *then* was paired with two special crystals - A Golden Lepidolite-Included Quartz Cathedral, and a Rainbow-Included Clear Quartz Orb. 

The first collector of this work will receive the physical crystals shown in this artwork! Please reach out to me to arrange your free shipment. For a more detailed look at the crystals, check out the video linked in the description.
